data.description: Welcome to your dream family home, nestled in an idyllic location with breathtaking views of the Big Lake! This stunning property offers an expansive layout featuring 3 true bedrooms and 2.5 luxurious baths, ensuring ample space for everyone. Step inside to find a welcoming ambiance flooded with natural light, complementing the tasteful decor and high-quality finishes throughout. The spacious living area opens up to a large kitchen, fully equipped with modern appliances and ample cabinetry—a perfect setup for home-cooked meals or casual get-togethers. For your convenience, this home comes with a full-sized, 2-car garage offering plenty of room for storage or your vehicles. Location is key, and this home has it all. Situated centrally, you're just minutes away from top-rated schools, making morning routines a breeze. Additionally, enjoy the proximity to diverse shopping options, the YMCA, and a variety of entertainment venues, ensuring you'll never run out of things to do. Don't miss this opportunity to secure a home that offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and luxury. Schedule your private tour today and come see for yourself what makes this property so special!
